You’ll Never Walk Alone - Limited Edition 7” Vinyl. 

From the new documentary film about Liverpool FC “The End Of The Storm”

All proceeds from the sale of the vinyl will go to charity, via the Liverpool FC Foundation..

All done happily in part w @bentap77

node.text: You see Joe, it’s times like this as the marine layer lifts off the sea on the dock with our candle lit- that I think to myself–  there are things that you still don’t know about me- like sometimes I’m afraid my sadness is too big - and that one day, you might have to help me handle it.
